Package gov.nyc.doitt.gis.geoclient.service.search.policy

Class SearchPolicy

java.lang.Object
gov.nyc.doitt.gis.geoclient.service.search.policy.SearchPolicy
public class SearchPolicy extends Object
Instances of this class are used to determine what constitutes an exact match and how many levels of sub-searching may be performed when the initial search criteria are rejected.
